你想怎樣
What do you want?

1091
01:29:20,480 --> 01:29:22,320
我想要知道巴爾的朋友是誰
l want to know who Barr's friends were.

1092
01:29:26,480 --> 01:29:27,610
這幫傢伙
Those boys out there,

1093
01:29:28,860 --> 01:29:31,660
