Be that as it may, l'm the only one
who's bothered to track him this far.

1100
01:29:48,210 --> 01:29:51,840
你幫我一次 我幫你解決債務問題
You help me out, l'll be in your debt.

1101
01:29:52,220 --> 01:29:53,310
