l'll answer one question.

1115
01:32:47,350 --> 01:32:48,690
誰是最好的射手
Who's your best shooter?

1116
01:32:50,190 --> 01:32:51,400
詹姆斯-巴爾
James Barr.

1117
01:32:54,900 --> 01:32:57,650
聽到他打死人 就把這些摘下來了
l pulled all these down
