ls this Reacher?

1204
01:39:50,940 --> 01:39:52,060
你是誰
Who is this?

1205
01:39:55,280 --> 01:39:57,620
我是雷徹
ls this Reacher?

1206
01:40:02,450 --> 01:40:05,580
是你 車裡的人
