You'll bounce me around
to make sure l'm not followed,

1213
01:40:22,140 --> 01:40:24,610
讓我走進埋伏 殺掉我
then walk me into
an ambush and kill me.

1214
01:40:24,810 --> 01:40:26,980
你毀了我的驚喜
Aw, you ruined my surprise.

1215
