Prison? ln America?

1349
01:59:42,750 --> 01:59:46,930
能去美國監獄 就像住進養老院
A retirement home.
lf l go to prison at all.

1350
01:59:47,050 --> 01:59:48,220
你認為能逃脫罪名嗎
You think you're gonna walk?

1351
01:59:48,430 --> 01:59:51,100
你是個無家可歸的人 被通緝的殺人犯
You are a homeless drifter
wanted for murder.

1352
01:59:51,430 --> 01:59:55,780
